high_descs: Turn right move forward slightly then turn left and walk straight to the kitchen sink and face it
Pick up the potato from the bottom of the sink
Turn around and move forward slightly then turn right and move forward slightly then turn right and face the microwave
Place the potato in the microwave, heat and then remove the potato
Slightly look down at the sink to the right with the potato
Place the potato in the sink
anns.task_desc: Heat a potato from a sink

high_descs: Turn right and walk towards the fridge, then hang a left and walk over to the kitchen sink.
Pick up the potato out of the sink.
Turn around and walk forward, then turn right and walk towards the door, turn right again to face the microwave.

Open the microwave and put the potato inside then close the door and turn on the microwave, after a couple seconds open the microwave back up and take the now heated potato out, then close the microwave.
Put the heated potato back in the kitchen sink on the left side.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated potato in the kitchen sink.

high_descs: Go forward and cross the room to face the sink.
Pick the potato up from the sink.
Move to the left and face the microwave.
Put the potato in the microwave and shut the door and then take the potato out of the microwave and shut the door again.
Turn slightly to face the sink.
Put the potato in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated potato in the sink.
